{"title":"AAA","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/AAA-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"- Aneurisma aorta abdominal\\N2024","guid":"be_NlBS1mNCWrJscHGBdIQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen","guid":"-RcdWEP0tIjx83B_dBxatQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Definición","guid":"OhMUFL3gf4woVfDx3KtJkg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Dilatación focal de la aorta abdominal (>1.5× su diámetro normal).","guid":"bkJJk6GUsFyymmaitrcU0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"2. Clasificación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Suprarrenal","guid":"H3Qjb5_SGztqTgPfxemhBg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Infrarrenal","guid":"ub3mPsejkScZ4bigpePamg","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"3. Factores de riesgo\\N(FR):","guid":"jJR9T1yklxCPLqU0oeNflw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Edad avanzada ♂ (>65 años)","guid":"FRaBHk3OR7Jz5xdnM3ctkA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Tabaquismo","guid":"7PrcDv9TDzCyK_-ecSpRxQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"• HTA","guid":"dA8kmUR4W9-YET5jz-Mi5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"4. Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Asintomático (frecuente → hallazgo incidental).","guid":"QkNsjAArafSFnfgTuw8vmQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Sintomático → Dolor lumbar, masa abdominal pulsátil, soplo abdominal.","guid":"Q14zDfpizIzZbtntWum1oQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"5. Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Ecografía abdominal (mejor prueba inicial y confirmatoria).","guid":"ZTrY2KbGD-uXrZesuWppLQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Evaluar extensión del aneurisma.","guid":"zUIuR0uH0l9v8kfY-tQO-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"1","text":"6. Manejo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Aneurismas pequeños: Observación, seguimiento cercano, ↓ factores CV.","guid":"Bw79T4xmq683Twm1PT3UOg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Aneurismas >5.5 cm (♂) o >5 cm (♀) o de rápida expansión → Cirugía.","guid":"U8fJyqN-QU-TdJbbCxzhIw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Opciones\\Nquirúrgicas:","guid":"HVEQ02gLGckiTgiaHE8SOA","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Resección abierta con injerto.","guid":"m42hwTyzVAdPR6WMNzQtVA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• Colocación de stent endovascular (EVAR).","guid":"3azqOoWi82a-hHMC3k-yhQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"1","text":"7. Pronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Desfavorable si ocurre disección o ruptura.","guid":"skBVpj4TTDSL7Ks3_S_Phg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Ruptura de AAA → Dolor súbito, masa pulsátil, shock hipovolémico → Cirugía emergente.","guid":"gAYtvmTkJbLNHikWxFDpSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"8. Screening:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Todos los ♂ entre 65-75 años con historia de tabaquismo\\N→ Ecografía abdominal (1 vez).","guid":"jW2EXrWpsbQUc683rQ6OKA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"Aneurisma de aorta\\Nabdominal (AAA)","guid":"tWRlHiBNZ0uvXeIcfVI5kQ","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"1. Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Dilatación localizada de las 3 capas de la pared de la aorta abdominal\\N(íntima, media, adventicia) ≥3 cm (1).","guid":"gpvJNcXzDXqg5F8rD0q0SA","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"2. Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Incidencia máxima: 60-70 años (raro <50 años).","guid":"jwEFt1SCtNQet6Bx0lYGcQ","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• Sexo: ♂ > ♀ (∼2:1).","guid":"wbu08-hDLkWVTOv4B9YfUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"28","text":"3. Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Factores de\\Nriesgo (FR):","guid":"6IK3pjWUji_wa3viDGyf-w","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Tabaquismo (FR más importante)","guid":"AsFzccD_FGaOQUDb3tscbQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"• Edad avanzada","guid":"nAX3-g7qXhRo7zY1BKhEOg","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"• Aterosclerosis (ASCVD)","guid":"9IzOysIn9GqQDnsNPRBdYQ","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"• Hipercolesterolemia y HTA","guid":"Z1Gzd5sRizxh1mGlohbrmg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"• Historia familiar (+)","guid":"vphGx0Fdd21uXrQKsKE5Jw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"• Sexo masculino","guid":"M_w55dFrBf9Q0dNGARn7dA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"35","text":"• Trauma","guid":"xj9Zo0B5UaFdlnkcmE4fRA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"28","text":"4. Clasificación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Localización:","guid":"XRqW4RBRD9Ivkcjdq-MLCg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Infrarrenal (más común) → 1/3 de los aneurismas se extienden hacia las arterias ilíacas (1).","guid":"pcpeHlLFAtlhqwz7neavdA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Suprarrenal.","guid":"vLEeBdJg6KCvDsfCt3e2oA","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"• Forma:","guid":"0JFluCXVtf3rRJzZ_B30ug","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Sacular (esférico).","guid":"i-el4Hw3Phb0uM3ktVWtvA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Fusiforme (en huso).","guid":"3Mn_RvBlzo89hIvajdA9Gg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"9dphqAztOZoKTYxjcDT3rQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"1. Proceso inflamatorio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Inflamación + degeneración proteolítica de proteínas del tejido conectivo (ej. colágeno, elastina y/o células de músculo liso)\\Nen px de alto riesgo → ↓ integridad estructural de la pared aórtica → ensanchamiento del vaso.","guid":"H-1UbHJEQBMCsbX53c-avQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"2. Estrés mecánico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• ↑ presión arterial → acción sobre la pared debilitada → dilatación → posible ruptura.","guid":"IuXgGxgfU_v_BuV14pSI2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"3. Alteración del flujo sanguíneo:","guid":"IzwwrynvtoaWmBjEXIcXAQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Dilatación aneurismática → Disrupción del flujo laminar → Turbulencia.","guid":"K7qUacjDYS51pG3SDGly8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"4. Formación de trombos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Posible trombosis en el aneurisma → Tromboembolismo periférico.","guid":"3qw2fsub2rmHkG6rKjOeFA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"0","text":"Clínica","guid":"scV_G78N3LJENSyGglPGlA","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"1. Generalidades:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Frecuentemente asintomático o con síntomas inespecíficos.","guid":"giViOfTlXT8ez-yUeyCwXA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Hallazgo incidental en ecografía o TAC.","guid":"kr2GBRJeYsip1-ASIlgNnQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Complicaciones graves: Ruptura o disección","guid":"rZ9zD0G8sXMAUycmnyg-5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"59","text":"2. Síntomas clínicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Dolor lumbar.","guid":"SOA2orFwPCJytbnsv5962g","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Masa abdominal pulsátil a nivel o por encima del ombligo.","guid":"xQEzQfcbqh22VTTNHMNjZw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"• Soplo abdominal en la auscultación.","guid":"tq53Y8AdI0nmcf3X7-W-mQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"59","text":"3. Complicaciones\\Ntromboembólicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Trombosis periférica.","guid":"3m_ImSMJF7TIewosBHKPfg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Fenómenos aterotrombóticos distales (ej. síndrome del dedo azul, livedo reticularis).","guid":"2pFabLDNHkTOM_YtnV9-Ag","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• ↓ índice tobillo-brazo (ABI).","guid":"uOERuB3RdVsjCEmPOaCXrQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"VNuN5WXUl7iLYNCRB4SKQA","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"1. Confirmación diagnóstica:","guid":"rWx8G6rdMGeDJ5ASgDY1tA","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Imágenes → Diámetro aórtico >3 cm.","guid":"SGfNTfhP_CPUFX5rLUUPNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"2. Pacientes inestables:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Sospecha de AAA roto → Traslado inmediato a quirófano para cirugía de emergencia","guid":"roULNKql4LILPDGKIyBaQQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"• No retrasar tratamiento si se sospecha AAA en px hemodinámicamente inestable.","guid":"K2fbSH2oAOZvhJZO30qaKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"3. Laboratorio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"• No existen hallazgos de laboratorio específicos para AAA.","guid":"ehkiBOYd4MHJF8ysFOgC1A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes","guid":"XdPHmZeX5uI4WfBbOhnw3A","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"1. Ecografía abdominal\\N(formal o POCUS)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Mejor prueba inicial y\\Nconfirmatoria en:","guid":"TuW_BVvCKEXVBpBMQPus2w","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Px asintomáticos","guid":"iI3TdVWmL3mcrW18KyKffA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Px con dolor abdominal sin AAA conocido o sin FR para AAA.","guid":"H4gM3t0l_WdFLh-f01PrNA","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"• Determinar presencia, tamaño y extensión del aneurisma.","guid":"Uy4a9Tg3VC-_fBhygVQnWQ","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"• Detección y vigilancia.","guid":"bXkrXt_ZZZmvAXEn3hQnEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"81","text":"• Ecografía\\Nformal:","guid":"dDutsuWKq90J2rwMS8LXiA","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Obtener vistas longitudinales\\Ny transversales de:","guid":"ofaIVt5Z7ccv5rBI9hnIvg","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Aorta abdominal proximal, media y distal.","guid":"VMRGfKIHyud0Y-L1Pqa4FQ","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• Ambas arterias ilíacas comunes proximales.","guid":"NZ71hyFDfb5UUvpRTiFm9g","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"• Medir el diámetro anteroposterior (AP) de cada vaso.","guid":"awpLU4dCPySt9om_V0egzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"• Hallazgos de\\Nsoporte:","guid":"gY-cXnAlVNtggz_sBahAMQ","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Dilatación de la aorta ≥ 3 cm (1).","guid":"hdLa_WDhkPSSxi47ub4yBA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"• Presencia de trombo posible.","guid":"-1lrZAEJJPYAKljtecctnw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"81","text":"• Manejo:","guid":"dAsKDRWYxxrYqNXv_UBtdg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Si se observa un aneurisma grande (≥5.5 cm en ♂, ≥5 cm en ♀) en\\Npx con dolor abdominal → Referir inmediatamente para tratamiento.","guid":"6ZVb5srK8F_6h9i_m-netw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"80","text":"2. Angiografía por TAC de\\Nabdomen y pelvis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"KvM7oW_hEbXJUUmn5K-PNQ","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Modalidad de elección en px sintomáticos y para planificación pre-intervención.","guid":"G1GKlN8RejGU_bnq-3tCrg","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"• Confirmar diagnóstico cuando la ecografía no es posible en px asintomáticos.","guid":"wNt_NMFI71gV_K6ecqnHQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"• Evaluación detallada de la localización, tamaño y extensión del aneurisma,\\Nimplicación de vasos colaterales y presencia de trombo o ruptura.","guid":"ASJktA8OzawcejWrLhv61g","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"• Hallazgos de\\Nsoporte:","guid":"vC4ttJTHYvMAJaFrRAGVGQ","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• Dilatación de la aorta ≥ 3 cm, posible dilatación de vasos colaterales.","guid":"CEpd-QMMUF8BFDDBGKKEgQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• Distribución reducida del vasa vasorum.","guid":"8ZMdxgO9QT94dP2EBgo1EA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"• Trombo presente.","guid":"apDGRp3AFFrgAgfVb8v3lw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial","guid":"rxpY6bd8iJGNDL0SoofY4A","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"1. Localización:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"• AAA:","guid":"UiIjaH4d60MsOWzgdk143A","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Debajo de las arterias renales (más común).","guid":"4LWvb1hBGgFr6GlQvV3ClQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"• TAA:","guid":"VWCzkz6tTuQ12bVsHJ25FQ","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"• Aorta ascendente (más común).","guid":"Ks7biudiLJvrD36LInZllQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"106","text":"2. Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"• AAA:","guid":"XGK55zQBWe5NjPliOMsNPg","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Edad avanzada.","guid":"8dyVwutBijwCOfEWBVSmpA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Predomina en ♂.","guid":"DpARf6OmMFdyja5jQdzjng","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"• Más frecuente que TAA.","guid":"Ul6MkJi9SHpoIloXolY5rw","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"• TAA:","guid":"Q1TOOytbTJ3Wn-MobKorTw","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Edad avanzada.","guid":"HkTgaOblybeMIN3bEgSjeQ","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Predomina en ♂.","guid":"zlodxdN_FYUF5Pv-9RogKg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"106","text":"3. Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"• AAA:","guid":"HSuZGfyOU01Wu0O_J1VPlg","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Tabaquismo (FR más importante).","guid":"rfyzUL5JhMJ4A08XTffE9Q","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Aterosclerosis.","guid":"gZhDdL3nNk4HULYJ2YZomg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• Hipercolesterolemia y HTA.","guid":"tnH4edX9rhX6i7ieH3ArbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"120","text":"• TAA:","guid":"Xofpj0xtHlKHZpfGPEUdEg","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• HTA.","guid":"GjnS4Q4Stad3EocA7BYhCg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Válvula aórtica bicúspide.","guid":"6GZ6S4C76wvRK7MAdTkXFg","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"• Sífilis terciaria (11).","guid":"akQuYHNgI8nku-Ik9la70w","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"• Enfermedades del tejido conectivo (síndrome de\\NMarfan, síndrome de Ehlers-Danlos).","guid":"DtInqkIE2mEkvRUdbWmOgA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"• Trauma.","guid":"BjawT81XOjNsJYJHH86opA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"125","text":"• Tabaquismo.","guid":"cWq_iefVO6-NrJ8fjNsDUg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"106","text":"4. Características\\Nclínicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"• AAA:","guid":"iqOe9Uu08qToVgjW3mQDUg","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• Masa abdominal pulsátil.","guid":"HsoO0FavHPqdwlMyevtIIg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• Soplo en la auscultación.","guid":"tMsdr4RJ5iEu-_YH-FEsAw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• Dolor lumbar.","guid":"3RqR-7yJ8vgHQvBUHvqsPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"132","text":"• TAA:","guid":"2XvHynUcokdt60ey91Fg5g","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"• Sensación de presión en el tórax.","guid":"oCl5n0698QnLP1Srpq4Wqg","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"• Dolor en la espalda torácica.","guid":"MAjRz70T9S7bXJiKkjr0Ew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"106","text":"5. Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• AAA:","guid":"eihtmPNV87GZDoFH75Td5g","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• Ecografía abdominal (mejor prueba inicial y confirmatoria).","guid":"kv7tZbNUVmtD8Mec55QtCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"• TAA:","guid":"h7SFq0jV-0TSf5vseE-9cg","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Radiografía de tórax y angio-TAC de tórax.","guid":"azGQhTSuU1UJD5RwgGkZ2w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"106","text":"6. Terapia (indicaciones\\Nde reparación):","guid":"lAd_hE7cI1LjKO13vARAkw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• AAA:","guid":"KOgzH5ZNKkkWfPwlzGqaDQ","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• Diámetro ≥ 5.5 cm (♂); ≥ 5.0 cm (♀).","guid":"MopclbtPwSzo0p4dXJwM6w","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"• Tasa de expansión ≥ 0.5 cm/6 meses.","guid":"Cn4M71C92nWP_ybgzWZpPw","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"• Aneurisma sintomático.","guid":"eTsLfMPa5d0vKfw9B77Q7w","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"146","text":"• Complicaciones (ruptura, aneurisma sacular).","guid":"2bghE_1kybZzstf8TOv15w","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"145","text":"• TAA:","guid":"gTSKB3iEW5h7ku7-S9Nj9g","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Diámetro:","guid":"m-B8ZRR5WvMM3lgOPSA2eQ","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• Raíz aórtica y aorta ascendente ≥ 5.5 cm.","guid":"9PNHBV5DgwIj2zWSngYSkA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• Arco aórtico ≥ 5.5 cm.","guid":"PZWqVMR9-8M6DC1v5khvHA","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"• Aorta descendente ≥ 5. 5 cm.","guid":"-1i82sYPLVOemxZLxF8k9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"151","text":"• Tasa de expansión ≥ 0.3 cm/año en 2 años consecutivos o ≥ 0.5 cm en 1 año.","guid":"3VZaCQzq18JxX5VV4JEocQ","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"151","text":"• Aneurisma sintomático.","guid":"koes7FMokcdJhpN2q9oVOA","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"151","text":"• Complicaciones (ruptura).","guid":"hn1OKp3ny7n4Nmvvpe3s6w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"3ZwstqQZvujPS2VnHCl-sA","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"General","guid":"4BMEhD3LDy8oqpp4jkCqBw","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"1. Pacientes\\Nsintomáticos","guid":"seIKFRmZtzq-At0-js9yTg","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"• Consulta inmediata a cirugía vascular","guid":"6ZQV-KPZeylBbuM9EdSELw","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"• Sospecha/ruptura confirmada → Reparación de emergencia (<90 min)","guid":"M0PnUy_TXbtNA1oR6raU1Q","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"161","text":"• Signos de ruptura inminente → Reparación urgente,\\Nidealmente dentro de horario laboral (mejores resultados)","guid":"rqMq5GU0r1YkWYEgcmUFtw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"• Mantener PA estrictamente en parámetros normales","guid":"R29QQiWI5qhbU2BrDOvU4g","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"161","text":"• Consultar a anestesia","guid":"PpuKUQej6eL0wD6eHPKGsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"160","text":"2. Pacientes asintomáticos","guid":"3A0WRKJDTqFZTyx7iFZHqw","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Reparación electiva del aneurisma o vigilancia","guid":"TOs-DrDD63c48QGn8LBQpA","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"160","text":"3. Todos los pacientes","guid":"mFggUO6w3LcdugSIc9-y6g","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Reducción de riesgo cardiovascular","guid":"cariCXAeJFUjbpN3bYQXzQ","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• Cese de tabaquismo","guid":"owo0NxNcRQX3iUp_hrI-cQ","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"• Manejo adecuado de factores de riesgo ateroscleróticos\\N(HTA, DM, dislipidemia)","guid":"UysSRhbMxwGHyL0hFRdXEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"160","text":"4. Consulta a cirugía vascular e UCI para pacientes con AAA sintomático","guid":"tp66F8f3qvg-krr9NP3-dg","children":[]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"159","text":"Tratamiento invasivo:\\NReparación de AAA","guid":"Iaiim-0j0hgSQeuDwTfVow","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"1. Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• Reparación de emergencia: Pacientes inestables","guid":"-tybX9jEmHpiCXyOLBCf4g","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"• Reparación urgente: Ruptura inminente o AAA con filtración","guid":"kwc1Borfvxw304W8CV0s4w","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"• Reparación\\Nelectiva [13]:","guid":"29oDToHa54iU9GTRrCUl3w","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• Diámetro: ≥5.5 cm en hombres; ≥5.0 cm en mujeres","guid":"1f_OG5NQX5jAxFrs9IKKlQ","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"• Tasa de expansión: ≥0.5 cm/6 meses","guid":"aM6uhrA09vGcBD-U9lk0eA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"• Aneurisma sintomático","guid":"5OkSMGWJ1Yc7bRnd0NQ-7g","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"• Aneurisma sacular","guid":"jNE9AF4s5lqT6NbAMAKPAg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"174","text":"2. Procedimientos [1]:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Reparación\\NEndovascular (EVAR)","guid":"1cC5C2u6pX0-s8VhYWJvew","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Indicaciones: Preferido en aneurismas,\\Nespecialmente en pacientes de alto riesgo quirúrgico","guid":"BVvfW9ucAdtBPzUOCxT-SQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"• Procedimiento: Colocación de endoprótesis expandible\\Nmediante arterias femoral o ilíaca guiado por fluoroscopia","guid":"YYndqfMAlD0izFIDdDvyRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"Reparación quirúrgica\\Nabierta (OSR)","guid":"okF8Tubku47dCwQcTLbj3Q","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Aneurisma micótico o injerto infectado","guid":"tjjtYxbU998ugyA6qmTSLA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"• Endofuga persistente con crecimiento del saco aneurismático post-EVAR","guid":"jo5wOnpgKHuEyPDZxZ4lSg","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"• Contraindicaciones anatómicas para EVAR","guid":"A-nFjo6BeMY-lyP7lvyEXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"• Procedimiento: Laparotomía y reemplazo del segmento dilatado con prótesis tubular o en Y","guid":"xc6OfF8NAVLvB6aTrzH65A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"174","text":"Tratamiento conservador:\\NVigilancia sin reparación","guid":"y35J06v7VzZURzkTQot9wg","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"1. AAA pequeño (<5.5 cm en hombres, <5.0 cm en mujeres), asintomático","guid":"_J6TAa6DPXIR-y4piLIDAg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Observación con ecografía periódica para identificar tasa\\Nde expansión y disminuir riesgo de ruptura","guid":"5mVh-WhlvPP8RDO8Ahuptw","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"• Frecuencia de seguimiento depende del tamaño del aneurisma","guid":"2tZ3B4lEw56joQOhHLU6Zg","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"174","text":"Frecuencia de seguimiento para\\Nvigilancia de AAA [13]","guid":"4pSp2JoefalMHeCxWj_7sQ","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Diámetro máximo de la aorta abdominal\\NIntervalo de seguimiento recomendado","guid":"3fBsJ46pLptmdX_GnOkCIg","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"3–3.9 cm Ecografía cada 3 años (hombres)","guid":"HUEwFSpBzIkLFVG12ZeEeA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"4–4.4 cm Ecografía cada 12 meses (hombres)","guid":"XSwmbN83oFD5yI3s9ODqkg","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"≥5.0 cm Ecografía cada 6 meses (hombres)","guid":"cRrngqYbHL1BCbmfSyX4hg","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"≥4.5 cm Ecografía cada 6 meses (mujeres)","guid":"e2kTxzixNQNoaBM4L3C_9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"197","text":"• El monitoreo regular es esencial debido a que el tamaño y la tasa de\\Nexpansión del aneurisma son predictores importantes del riesgo de ruptura.","guid":"G5S_Y5CmItAapS3LaeFCLw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones del Aneurisma de\\NAorta Abdominal (AAA)","guid":"q_BOYUVMaUrbOk5CHwTA6w","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"1. Ruptura de AAA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"2. Embolismo → Material trombótico del aneurisma","guid":"MCVZDyLSAP55idlZgwJTJg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"3. Disección aórtica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"4. Complicaciones\\Npostoperatorias [19]:","guid":"8llV42Xf-yUuIeuQkWZGsg","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"• Isquemia intestinal, renal y medular","guid":"EO31mESht04VlsOjDGr_WQ","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"208","text":"• Oclusión de arteria espinal anterior","guid":"9rOW-NfmaqhjeZHvDY9ugQ","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"208","text":"• Infección del injerto protésico","guid":"Wa6wxIZFzAFNjreG0Y7Slw","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"208","text":"• Fístula aortoentérica","guid":"PD1ZI1XjTirh7bvIy_c_wA","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"208","text":"• Complicaciones\\Npost-EVAR [1]:","guid":"Iy5D0QOkKZBRINUgMzWeUA","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"• Endofuga","guid":"JeG0ZtvQeuuDkxwomByWgw","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"• Complicaciones en el sitio de acceso (sangrado, hematoma, pseudoaneurisma)","guid":"WCT9Zmy5mhMeaHOUf0crfQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"• Trombosis del injerto","guid":"Emqnl_SWOneumNMI4Fy7EQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"0","text":"Prevención del\\NAAA","guid":"7hs8XY9DbzFYp650NMKwug","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"1. Prevención\\Nprimaria [1]:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"• Cese de tabaquismo","guid":"KHdEm36ZALW-XASl8BwgfQ","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"• Ingesta regular de nueces, frutas y verduras (>3 veces/semana)","guid":"xisO6ZUK_MlZ3re1ofI4-w","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"• Ejercicio (>1 vez/semana)","guid":"wbCC_WMwmCU90ZvIxeG-5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"217","text":"2. Tamizaje de\\NAAA [1][2][13]:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"6OlNRQkpQuQT6Tab1rWabw","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"• Hombres de 65–75 años con antecedente de tabaquismo\\N(fumadores activos o previos)","guid":"Ro_Fr6h92O9Fiq0P1KeVKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"• Considerar en:","guid":"9aDpXG9M7jFUs6XoHkUIuQ","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"• Hombres de 65–75 años con historia familiar de AAA\\N(primer grado)","guid":"3fSZ70R79vzH2LGSr9u8hA","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"225","text":"• Mujeres de 65–75 años fumadoras","guid":"W4aZpxmZ4S0WamL5wKxjMQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"• Personas >75 años sin tamizaje previo y\\Nantecedentes de tabaquismo o historia familiar","guid":"9w5j1z4Fv0okek_m7VWqrg","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"225","text":"• <65 años con factores de riesgo\\Nmúltiples o historia familiar de AAA","guid":"GuntKOACjSoqKNHsyhY91A","children":[]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"222","text":"• Modalidad: Ecografía abdominal","guid":"mc8zokYeFpOqP534YKW8CQ","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"222","text":"• Frecuencia:","guid":"uyiBe53xsW5kYf-NhrjWxQ","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"• Tamizaje único recomendado","guid":"9JQnG73aNy9v6zLf0aHU9A","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"• Considerar repetir después de 10 años si\\Ndiámetro inicial entre 2.5–3 cm","guid":"2e6VG3C-i_mh_OuE4VtRhQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"0","text":"Ruptura de Aneurisma de\\NAorta Abdominal (AAA)","guid":"TdKrN9wFG9uyI53_7mtEFg","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"1. Factores de riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Expansión rápida del aneurisma","guid":"tNvlOHRBGZAlpx_ynGR4rg","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"• Aneurisma de gran diámetro","guid":"qBlFJ36j27J_UZ9uXe3O4Q","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"235","text":"• Tabaquismo","guid":"wlV3d7zRo6s-X1xo35RInQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"2. Características\\Nclínicas","guid":"uLRsxIbhgJ9--OZrSo8Vrw","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"• Triada\\Nclásica","guid":"G7JB9mj5NCV7MKmBC80JJA","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"• Hipotensión por shock hipovolémico\\N(frecuente en rupturas libres)","guid":"C3jYGek0D85ePZ2DkUXgfA","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"• Dolor abdominal o lumbar súbito, severo,\\Ncon irradiación a flanco, piernas o ingle","guid":"YJN4YzEj0QqH-y7vVoB3rQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"• Masa pulsátil dolorosa","guid":"0nTUlT2bumEZVm7Mo1Olsw","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"239","text":"• Signos de Grey Turner y/o Cullen\\N(hematoma retroperitoneal extenso)","guid":"P_FoTrjX8g88-UaPz43faQ","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"239","text":"• Náuseas, vómitos","guid":"nxOtXtRUjbIer0m0SHTK9Q","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"239","text":"• Síncope","guid":"Qd132R2KnM7pxryLyFiWiw","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"239","text":"• Hematuria","guid":"6LthLLz8UbjGt_-vLao5OQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"234","text":"3. Diagnóstico","guid":"1bs0srzVRqE0UamhERq9Yw","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"• Pacientes inestables → Diagnóstico clínico, referir directamente a tratamiento quirúrgico","guid":"-ADAp0QpjvUU8mNrYtfKBg","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"• Pacientes estables\\N(controversial)","guid":"Oy8_Cs1Rv5ebjUDmjlkZpA","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"• Considerar imágenes en consulta con cirugía\\Nvascular si no retrasa el tratamiento","guid":"oxgGIw7zUwZHivWqSRv4RA","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"• Evaluar otras etiologías o realizar evaluación\\Nanatómica (CTA toracoabdominal) para EVAR","guid":"QpJg9VSIJUF-HRPkz12HHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"234","text":"4. Modalidades\\Nde imagen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"• CTA (Tórax,\\Nabdomen, pelvis)","guid":"6mpU-WfWx7HLwVess56Low","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Estudio de elección si no retrasa la cirugía","guid":"ewOcZa3rdtWo2fAcv5KzPQ","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"• Alta detección de ruptura contenida y sangrado retroperitoneal","guid":"NQcBPR2E3hyEy9XpcJyP3g","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"• Hallazgos:","guid":"5O3Xb6YWZZt2A9Qnd_FEGg","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"• Signo de ruptura inminente → Crescente de alta atenuación en trombo mural","guid":"l0tdMeVCK4jZnwI77c7h4A","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"• Signos de ruptura → Hematoma retroperitoneal, extravasación de contraste","guid":"rS15sy6hplnqeLt9z8PgRA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"253","text":"• POCUS (Paciente inestable) → Dilatación aórtica ≥3 cm → AAA hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"zvCNbdVbMcDtrLnvmQEtng","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"234","text":"5. Estudios adicionales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"• Laboratorio","guid":"xPNnR7sU1Hd2oG3mCpCFfA","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• CBC: ↓ hemoglobina, ↓ hematocrito, ↓ recuento de eritrocitos","guid":"FbnbpL8KVFzXz5NhIrrQ2g","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"• Acidosis metabólica en shock","guid":"-mJGLKy_jZzwUkUwujcJjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"265","parent":"261","text":"• ECG → Cambios isquémicos por pérdida aguda de sangre","guid":"jukOVRU7EKbhl0V8_NzWSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"234","text":"6. Tratamiento\\N[1][12]","guid":"FbVhdZ---I--kXu_Xc7fcw","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Manejo inicial (30\\Nmin)","guid":"9piYNy33nQp4XjDYPAi4Pg","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"• Acceso IV de gran calibre","guid":"N9e9a9SM97dZq-w99YOAIw","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"• Monitoreo continuo y reevaluación frecuente","guid":"IizcbSc0nIwk6p8R9fiAOQ","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"267","text":"• Soporte hemodinámico inmediato","guid":"glLQ4OyK2MN-ATxvdEuQJA","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"267","text":"• Resucitación con fluidos o transfusión sanguínea","guid":"NhFpQsyURPOii06-efPQMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"266","text":"• Objetivo: Hipotensión permisiva (PAS 70–90 mm Hg)","guid":"GaAKLUe3NrnxPrDxCIBnvA","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"266","text":"• Tratamiento definitivo (90 min) → EVAR o OSR de emergencia","guid":"Xooz13iDB9lY7UY_i_xQpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"234","text":"7. Pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• Alta mortalidad (~81%)","guid":"hq_EfIXecg1xB3Hk9OUbPQ","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"• Edad avanzada, pérdida de conciencia, paro\\Ncardíaco antes de cirugía → Mortalidad alta","guid":"DqduyTaOHMdXWEU3ytBSkQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":276,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"AAA-2024","id":"map_697","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"AAA-2024"}